        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2038278595" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7753425919112626869">Definitely a book to read if you have some level of seriousness in becoming a doctor. The diaries help you to get a true understanding of how grueling being a first-year resident is even though the three interns are all involved in pediatrics.<br/><br/>I only read the first 145 pages of this book and then stopped because even though I wanted to see the transformation the 3 Interns go through there comes a point when you only need to hear so many stories to understand how grueling the residency process is.</span>
  <span id="freeText7753425919112626869" style="display:none">Definitely a book to read if you have some level of seriousness in becoming a doctor. The diaries help you to get a true understanding of how grueling being a first-year resident is even though the three interns are all involved in pediatrics.<br /><br />I only read the first 145 pages of this book and then stopped because even though I wanted to see the transformation the 3 Interns go through there comes a point when you only need to hear so many stories to understand how grueling the residency process is.<br /><br />The one thing that really shocked me that all readers I think will appreciate is the level of detail that is seen in the diary entries.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7753425919112626869" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


