<div id="review_4403787699" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4403787699" />
    <a title="Marie Clark" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/39984016-marie-clark"><img alt="Marie Clark" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1626105812p2/39984016.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4403787699?book_show_action=true">Dec 22, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Marie Clark" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Marie Clark" href="/user/show/39984016-marie-clark">Marie Clark</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4403787699" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11105513657107129492">Super happy I read this book. Kevin recommended it and it was a great glimpse into the life of a pediatric intern in the 80s. Some things have changed and others have not. Following the lives of 3 different doctors and all the units they were learning on and challenges was interesting. I liked the humor and voice of the people in this voice recorded transcription. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

