              <span id="reviewTextContainer3213421779" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16356705670143132623">This is an excellent book to let people know about the true experiences of men and women doing their year of medical internship. The medical language is explained, as the young adults describe their best and worst days (and nights) on and off the job. </span>

          </span>
